    "name": "Bantu",
    "epitet": "Tiki's Guardian",
    "display": "Bantu: Tiki's Guardian",
    "description": "A manakete of the Fire Dragon clan, and Tiki's guardian. He released Tiki from the Ice Dragon Temple, where she had been kept hidden away. Appears in Fire Emblem: Mystery of the Emblem.",
    "artist": "Yamada Akihiro (山田章博)",
    "voiceActorEN": "Joe J. Thomas",
    "voiceActorJP": "小西克幸",
    "lowestRarity": 3,
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "Excuse me... Have you met a young girl by the name of Tiki?",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "I could not bear to keep Tiki locked away from the world, but in freeing her, much misfortune arose...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Hm? Me? I am Bantu. They call me a fire dragon.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I am sturdier than I look. You needn't worry yourself on my account.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Tiki is of the Divine Dragon Naga's tribe. To defeat an evil dragon, her power will be necessary...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "This world is new—and strange... Would you be so kind as to help me find Tiki?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You there... Do you happen to know a young girl by the name of Tiki? I've heard rumors here and there...",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "I may not be much of a dragon, but... I will not fall behind! Not so long as this stone remains in my— Oh... Er...",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Battle...would be best avoided.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "...I will survive.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Rather reckless of you... Do not blame me if my power grows out of control.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "You are a curious human. I have lived a long life, but...never before have I encountered one such as you. Yet it feels as if... No, it's not possible you and I have met...is it? Perhaps you only remind me of someone... Whatever the case, I have a favor to ask of you: Would you take care of this dragonstone for me? It need not be right away; I must keep watch over Tiki, after all. Yet the time will come when my duty ends... When that time comes...I will leave quietly and dispense of the dragon in me, as my brethren before me...",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
